Brewing science models
  Calculation models (IBU: Tinseth/Rager/Garetz/Daniels; color: Morey/Mosher/
  Daniels; yeast viability decline curves; carbonation and residual CO2) are
  implementations of published formulas; sources are cited inline in the
  relevant source files under src/lib/brewing/.

